{"article_id":"Ipscw8ogVlKpXzKM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"With his pledge","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"to save a major Chinese company from crippling US sanctions ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump has delivered yet another twist in the trade clash with Beijing .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"His announcement on Twitter","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that he 's working to give China 's ZTE `` a way","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to get back into business , fast ''","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"was a sudden shift in the US stance at the start of a big week for trade ties between the world 's top two economies .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Washington and Beijing have threatened to impose tariffs on tens of billions of dollars of each other 's products ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"fueling fears of a full-blown trade war .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Related :","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"Trump says","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"he 's working with China","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to save ZTE","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Talks in Beijing earlier this month","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"aimed at dialing down the tensions","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"failed to produce any major breakthroughs .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"But Chinese President Xi Jinping 's top economic adviser is heading to Washington this week for more negotiations .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"American companies will also have a chance","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to publicly tell the Trump administration what they think about its planned tariffs on Chinese goods .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The fate of Chinese technology company ZTE","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"( ZTCOF )","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"has become a major flashpoint in the US-China trade tensions .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Last month , the US Commerce Department blocked American firms from selling parts or providing services to ZTE ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"which makes smartphones and other telecommunications equipment .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"The ban was put in place","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"after Washington said","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"ZTE violated a deal","depth":14},{"id":27,"text":"in which the Chinese company agreed to pay a $ 1.2 billion fine","depth":15},{"id":28,"text":"for evading US sanctions on Iran and North Korea .","depth":15},{"id":29,"text":"Related :","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"ZTE is now center stage in the US-China trade fight","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"ZTE ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"which employs around 75,000 people worldwide ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"has disputed the decision","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"and is appealing it .","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"The company upped the stakes last week","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"by saying","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"it had halted most of its operations","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"because of the ban .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Trump appeared to throw ZTE a lifeline with his tweet Sunday","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"in which he said","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"`` too many '' Chinese jobs were at risk .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"The Commerce Department has been `` instructed '' to get ZTE back into business ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"he added .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump 's announcement","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"-- welcomed Monday by Beijing --","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"should create a more positive backdrop for trade talks .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"`` The Trump administration is softening its stance","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and stepping back from using the most destructive weapon in the negotiation , ''","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"said Ken Cheung , a currency strategist at Mizuho Bank in Hong Kong .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"`` The second round of negotiation should be more constructive . ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Chinese Vice Premier Liu He will lead a Chinese delegation","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"visiting Washington from Tuesday through Saturday ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"China 's Foreign Ministry said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"`` I suspect","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Liu will try to engage with his Treasury counterpart , Steven Mnuchin ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"whom the Chinese see as the most willing to make a deal , ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"said Richard McGregor , senior fellow at the Lowy Institute , a think tank","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"based in Sydney .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Related :","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"China says","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"'big differences ' remain after US trade talks","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"The scale of the challenge","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"facing negotiators","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"was highlighted by a widely reported list of demands","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that the US delegation gave to the Chinese government before the first round of talks .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"It included cutting the US trade deficit with China by $ 200 billion by the end of 2020 and halting Chinese subsidies for advanced technology industries .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"McGregor , an expert on Chinese politics and international relations , said","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"he does n't think","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Liu will offer any big concessions on the trade deficit ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"but will rather focus on measures","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"to open up China 's markets to more American investment .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"While Liu is in Washington ,","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"American companies will be airing their views on the Trump administration 's plan","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"to slap tariffs on around $ 50 billion worth of Chinese goods as punishment for alleged intellectual property theft .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Among the big US companies","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that have asked to testify at the hearings","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"are Best Buy","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"( BBY ) ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"HP","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"( HPQ )","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"and US Steel","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"( X ) .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Lobbying groups","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"seeking to take part","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"include the National Retail Federation and the National Association of Manufacturers .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"The hearings start Tuesday","depth":3},{"id":87,"text":"and are scheduled to last three days .","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"The US government has published a list of 1,300 Chinese exports","depth":3},{"id":89,"text":"that it plans to target with tariffs of 25 % , many of them in advanced manufacturing industries such as aerospace .","depth":3},{"id":90,"text":"Related :","depth":3},{"id":91,"text":"Who likes tariffs ?","depth":4},{"id":92,"text":"Generally , it 's not the same people","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"who like Trump","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"US Trade Representative Robert Lighthizer has expressed particular concern about Beijing 's high-tech ambitions ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"as outlined in a Chinese government plan","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"known as `` Made in China 2025 . ''","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"A number of big US businesses and industry associations have opposed the planned tariffs ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"fearing higher costs for American consumers and retaliation from China .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"China has already hit back","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"by proposing its own tariffs on American goods","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"worth a similar amount .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":189,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":187,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":114,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":110,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nucle